headline: Willis Towers Watson Public : WTW secures Kingdom of Saudi Arabia (K.S.A.) reinsurance license and appoints New Head of Reinsurance Broking
summary: LONDON, January 20, 2025 - WTW , a leading global advisory, broking, and solutions company, today announced it has secured a licence to act as a reinsurance broker in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia . ...
